{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2ff1c7ae26","title":"大字报——反对不按劳取酬","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2c671ff346","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"2ff1c7ae26"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"545135ab5a","name":"匿名"},{"id":"b9d6e9c96b","name":"北京政法学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"94913d9bfa","type":"title","text":"大字报——反对不按劳取酬","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ff1c7ae26"},{"id":"c30301a1da","type":"authors","text":"北京政法学院匿名","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ff1c7ae26"},{"id":"bb4c495435","type":"paragraph","text":"我们看了刺头同志写的“某某老婆”工资表，感到很气愤，这些夫人太太们有很多是工作不称职的，反而领取高薪，象徐敬之老婆赵淑云、侯冠儒老婆郭素贞等人，大字不识几个，写几句话都写不通，居然也领取比大学教师高宝华等人还高的工资，这简直是浪费国家财产，我们坚决反对这种按丈夫官职资格取酬的原则！我们建议：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ff1c7ae26"},{"id":"47dfd358ea","type":"paragraph","text":"一、结合整风精简行政机构，将那些不适合工作的官太太们和其他人调到其他工作岗位上去。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ff1c7ae26"},{"id":"96e1acae79","type":"paragraph","text":"二、那些能力低，工资高的太太们和其他人应降低工资，实行按劳取酬。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ff1c7ae26"},{"id":"d126925b9e","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《北京政法学院右派分子言行汇编》(第3部分)(北京政法学院，1957年10月)。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ff1c7ae26"}],"page":{"id":"8e0b5dc331","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ff1c7ae26","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}